{"tid":1139661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可怕！愛滋醫生惡意使用汙染針頭 90人感染AIDS","createTime":"2019-05-05T12:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T09:21:03.000Z","uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a89865bbb49d58f27716cde0a47d96d523ab1437","tid":1139661,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"太可惡了！巴基斯坦醫生穆查法（Muzaffar Ghanghar）在信德省拉爾卡納（Larkana）一間公立醫院工作，孰料染有愛滋的他竟疑似故意使用受汙染的針頭，讓至少90人感染到AIDS，其中有65人是兒童。<br />\n <br />\n綜合外媒報導，本月初當地愛滋病例開始爆增，引起民眾恐慌，警方介入調查後認為穆查法涉有重嫌，便以散播HIV病毒的罪嫌將他逮捕偵訊。<br />\n <br />\n信德省衛生部長佩丘（Azra Pechuho）表示，受感染兒童的父母的血液也經過測試，但結果全都是陰性，可見並非是父母的問題。<br />\n <br />\n穆查法對此辯稱，這一切都是信德省醫療保健委員會為了對付他所設計的陰謀，他根本不知道自己感染了AIDS，如果知道的話就會去看醫生，更何況他沒有出現任何症狀。目前穆查法仍被關押在拘留所，等待進一步的調查。"},{"pid":"b7ae71aaf1290d8a9ece1a936603dbab1b4521f5","tid":1139661,"uid":182933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8d34ed83de620a84242c14ce4203ecda268cda7","tid":1139661,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7ae71aaf1290d8a9ece1a936603dbab1b4521f5","tid":1139661,"uid":182933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:29:13.000Z","msg":"唔死得，轉做志願生化武器賺外滙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b147efb5c036dd4b435a26b93d0f959dafaa71","tid":1139661,"uid":33731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/JipHeST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJipHeST.jpg&h=d346454b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42362919f15967fd3ca8690137f13928fd811895","tid":1139661,"uid":95494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"